07:20.774 --> 07:24.027
he left this box.

07:26.446 --> 07:29.533
He told me l could
hold it...

07:29.575 --> 07:32.828
'til he could make up
his back rent.

07:36.790 --> 07:40.043
Do you have any idea
where he might be now ?

07:40.085 --> 07:43.547
You might try checking down
at Our Lady of Charity.

07:43.589 --> 07:45.549
Marine, huh ?

07:45.591 --> 07:47.885
Ah, Recon.

07:47.926 --> 07:50.762
- l was in the service
for a while myself.
- Really ?

07:50.846 --> 07:53.265
- Yeah.
- Do you know him ?

07:53.348 --> 07:55.767
Well, he comes here
sometimes.

07:55.809 --> 07:58.770
Nice guy too.
Uh, if l see him,

07:58.854 --> 08:01.899
l'll-- l'll tell him
you're looking.

08:01.940 --> 08:04.693
Do you happen to know
where he lives ?

08:08.989 --> 08:12.451
l-l'm afraid your--
Your daddy, uh, well--

08:12.492 --> 08:15.454
Well, he was like the rest of us:
out of doors.

08:15.537 --> 08:17.456
You know ?

08:47.903 --> 08:50.322
How is that gumbo, Chance ?

08:52.157 --> 08:54.076
A tragedy.

08:54.159 --> 08:56.119
The coffee
was tolerable, though.

08:56.161 --> 08:59.748
- lt ain't free neither.
- Yeah, l know.

08:59.832 --> 09:02.251
Leave your wallet
in your tuxedo ?

09:04.169 --> 09:06.338
l play that one
on you before ?

09:06.380 --> 09:10.968
- Yeah. For the gumbo.
- That's right.

