please let me know

09:51.133 --> 09:54.595
But if you don't
want me that bad

09:54.678 --> 09:57.890
Darlin'
please let me know

10:06.273 --> 10:08.567
Hi, Murray.

10:08.609 --> 10:11.778
Yes, l was wondering if my father
came to pick up his mail yet.

10:13.071 --> 10:16.909
He hasn't ? No, that's fine.
Thank you. Bye-bye.

10:31.465 --> 10:34.259
- Hello, pretty lady.
- Leave me the hell alone.

10:34.301 --> 10:36.929
We'll take the wallet.

10:37.012 --> 10:39.765
How about a little
extra, honey ?

10:43.936 --> 10:46.438
You having fun ?

10:52.110 --> 10:56.031
Why don't you do yourself
a favor, boy ?

10:56.114 --> 11:00.410
l think the favor
gonna be done for you.

11:00.452 --> 11:03.622
lt's okay.

11:03.705 --> 11:06.625
l said get lost.

11:09.169 --> 11:13.131
Now, take your big stick
and your boyfriend...

11:13.215 --> 11:15.884
and find a bus to catch.

11:15.968 --> 11:18.595
Oh, this guy's funny.

11:53.672 --> 11:56.175
Come on, let's go !

12:23.243 --> 12:26.121
